spanGrp.span: Well, I grew up in Edikisa.
Edikisa is a very beautiful village.
edditänä kissä var güzäl ziaratlar var razni ziaratlar
There was a beautiful park and a fountain.
o kövümüzdä varıdi güzäl park varıdi fantan
ee sora orda var čoğ güzäl pıharlar
We have even our spring called Cold Spring.
daže pıharımız var adi šei soyuh pıhardır
The nature is very beautiful of that village.
čoğ güzäl prirodasi var o kövün
